{
  "title": "是鞍山，不是洛杉矶（二）",
  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "html": "鞍山新<span class=\"vocab\">楼盘<span class=\"tooltip\">lóu pán — real estate project</span></span>的房价大约五千到一万，然而台町这些老房子，<span class=\"vocab\">均价<span class=\"tooltip\">jūn jià — average price</span></span>则上了两万，<span class=\"vocab\">妥妥的<span class=\"tooltip\">tuǒ tuǒ de — definitely; for sure</span></span>高级住宅区了。现在这一带许多别墅<span class=\"vocab\">小院<span class=\"tooltip\">xiǎo yuàn — small courtyard</span></span>也改为咖啡店、餐厅什么的，<span class=\"vocab\">氛围<span class=\"tooltip\">fēn wéi — atmosphere</span></span>感非常好。我问了一位老板，他租了一间带房子的两层小楼，年租也就8万<span class=\"vocab\">而已<span class=\"tooltip\">ér yǐ — that's all; nothing more</span></span>。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN%202-1.mp4",
      "image": { "src": "img/p2_1.jpg" }
    },
    {
      "html": "鞍山的咖啡文化浓厚，以这样<span class=\"vocab\">量级<span class=\"tooltip\">liàng jí — magnitude; scale</span></span>的城市，咖啡店竟然很<span class=\"vocab\">密集<span class=\"tooltip\">mì jí — dense; intensive</span></span>，而且<span class=\"vocab\">质量<span class=\"tooltip\">zhì liàng — quality</span></span>非常高，这倒是让我比较意外。鞍山咖啡<span class=\"vocab\">风气之盛<span class=\"tooltip\">fēng qì zhī shèng — prosperity of a trend</span></span>，<span class=\"vocab\">国外<span class=\"tooltip\">guó wài — foreign</span></span>咖啡<span class=\"vocab\">巨头<span class=\"tooltip\">jù tóu — giant (company, leader)</span></span>也注意到了，前两年 Tims 跨出大连在东北<span class=\"vocab\">扩展<span class=\"tooltip\">kuò zhǎn — expand</span></span>，第一间店不是开在像哈尔滨、长春、沈阳等地，竟然选在鞍山。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN%202-2.mp4",
      "image": { "src": "img/p2_2.jpg" }
    },
    {
      "html": "鞍山几间有名的咖啡店，几乎都是风格强烈的街角小店，像芝士份子咖啡店，开店十年，应该是鞍山最早做<span class=\"vocab\">精品<span class=\"tooltip\">jīng pǐn — boutique; high-quality goods</span></span>咖啡的，客人<span class=\"vocab\">来来往往<span class=\"tooltip\">lái lái wǎng wǎng — coming and going</span></span>，好像都很熟了。类似的<span class=\"vocab\">独立<span class=\"tooltip\">dú lì — independent</span></span>小咖啡店，都在很认真地做咖啡。在“咖啡市”上海，什么都讲究<span class=\"vocab\">效率<span class=\"tooltip\">xiào lǜ — efficiency</span></span>，你几乎找不到一间店，简单的 18 元冰美式，还能摆着漂漂亮亮的<span class=\"vocab\">盘饰<span class=\"tooltip\">pán shì — plate decoration</span></span>给你<span class=\"vocab\">端<span class=\"tooltip\">duān — carry with both hands</span></span>过来。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN%202-3.mp4",
      "image": { "src": "img/p2_3.jpg" }
    },
    {
      "html": "<span class=\"vocab\" data-pinyin=\"shí zhí\" data-english=\"at that time\">时值</span><span class=\"vocab\" data-pinyin=\"shài qiū cài\" data-english=\"dry autumn vegetables in the sun\">晒秋菜</span>季节，在东北，一间<span class=\"vocab\" data-pinyin=\"shè qū\" data-english=\"community\">社区</span>咖啡店能不能与邻居<span class=\"vocab\" data-pinyin=\"dǎ chéng yī piàn\" data-english=\"integrate well\">打成一片</span>，通常不在于咖啡，而在于有没有场地给大家晒大白菜。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN%202-4.mp4"
    },
    {
      "html": "鞍山明显比东北相同<span class=\"vocab\">量级<span class=\"tooltip\">liàng jí — magnitude; scale</span></span>的城市<span class=\"vocab\">有活力<span class=\"tooltip\">huó lì — vitality; energy</span></span>得多，当然在很大<span class=\"vocab\">程度<span class=\"tooltip\">chéng dù — degree; extent</span></span>上是因为<span class=\"vocab\">伟大<span class=\"tooltip\">wěi dà — great; grand</span></span>的鞍钢还在<span class=\"vocab\">运作<span class=\"tooltip\">yùn zuò — operate</span></span>，据说鞍山现在 GDP 有 70% 都是鞍钢给<span class=\"vocab\">贡献<span class=\"tooltip\">gòng xiàn — to contribute</span></span>的。鞍钢<span class=\"vocab\">钢铁厂<span class=\"tooltip\">gāng tiě chǎng — steel mill</span></span><span class=\"vocab\">围绕<span class=\"tooltip\">wéi rào — surround</span></span>着市区 1/3，我找到高处眺望：住宅楼<span class=\"vocab\">边缘<span class=\"tooltip\">biān yuán — edge; margin</span></span>的<span class=\"vocab\">高架路<span class=\"tooltip\">gāo jià lù — elevated road</span></span>，后头鞍钢的厂区的<span class=\"vocab\">烟囱<span class=\"tooltip\">yān cōng — chimney</span></span>，又是洛杉矶城市<span class=\"vocab\">边缘<span class=\"tooltip\">biān yuán — edge; margin</span></span>工业区内味儿。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN%202-5.mp4",
      "image": { "src": "img/p2_4.jpg" }
    },
    {
      "html": "前几个月我去了<span class=\"vocab\">柳州<span class=\"tooltip\">liǔ zhōu — Liuzhou (city in China)</span></span>，在一间杂货店买东西问路，咦，奇怪！老板怎么是东北口音？后来一问才知道，他以前是从鞍山过来<span class=\"vocab\">支援<span class=\"tooltip\">zhī yuán — support; assist</span></span>柳钢<span class=\"vocab\">建设<span class=\"tooltip\">jiàn shè — construction; build</span></span>的，就在柳州<span class=\"vocab\">安家<span class=\"tooltip\">ān jiā — settle down</span></span>了。这么说吧，后来中国那些有名的钢铁厂：包钢、武钢、攀钢、酒钢、宝钢、首钢、柳钢……基本就是鞍钢的人给<span class=\"vocab\">整<span class=\"tooltip\">zhěng — put together; organize</span></span>出来的……<span class=\"vocab\">可惜<span class=\"tooltip\">kě xī — unfortunately; it's a pity</span></span>当年不能<span class=\"vocab\">控股<span class=\"tooltip\">kòng gǔ — hold shares</span></span>。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN%202-6.mp4"
    },
    {
      "html": "鞍钢<span class=\"vocab\">体量<span class=\"tooltip\">tǐ liàng — size; volume</span></span>之<span class=\"vocab\">庞大<span class=\"tooltip\">páng dà — huge</span></span>，各种<span class=\"vocab\">产业<span class=\"tooltip\">chǎn yè — industry</span></span>基本<span class=\"vocab\">承包<span class=\"tooltip\">chéng bāo — undertake</span></span>鞍山生活的<span class=\"vocab\">方方面面<span class=\"tooltip\">fāng fāng miàn miàn — all aspects</span></span>，生老病死应该都能<span class=\"vocab\">沾上边<span class=\"tooltip\">zhān shàng biān — be connected with</span></span>。举个例子，鞍山的朋友推荐我试试他们从小喝到大的“鞍钢鲜奶”，是鞍钢<span class=\"vocab\">自有<span class=\"tooltip\">zì yǒu — own; self-run</span></span><span class=\"vocab\">牧场<span class=\"tooltip\">mù chǎng — ranch; pasture</span></span>生产的。这种鲜奶在一般的<span class=\"vocab\">便利店<span class=\"tooltip\">biàn lì diàn — convenience store</span></span>、超市还买不到，你要下午三点左右，到比较热闹的街上，幸运的话会遇到这种推着车卖鞍钢<span class=\"vocab\">乳业<span class=\"tooltip\">rǔ yè — dairy industry</span></span>各种产品的阿姨。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN%202-7.mp4"
      "image": { "src": "img/p2_5.jpg" }
    }
  ],
